<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>
  XQ Tech Solutions ("we," "our," or "us") operates the Field Fresh Milk mobile application
  (the "App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard
  your information when you use Field Fresh Milk.
</p>
<p>
  Field Fresh Milk is a dairy and milk delivery app for homes plus a management tool for
  local vendors — covering subscriptions, daily delivery routes, and payments.
</p>
<p>
  By using Field Fresh Milk, you agree to the collection and use of information in
  accordance with this Privacy Policy.
</p>

<hr />

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>1. User Profile Information</h3>
<p>When you register and use Field Fresh Milk, we collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and password</li>
  <li><strong>Profile Details:</strong> Profile photo (optional) and account preferences</li>
  <li><strong>Delivery Address:</strong> Street address, locality, and pincode for milk delivery</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Vendor Information</h3>
<p>If you register as a local milk vendor on the App, we additionally collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Vendor Profile:</strong> Vendor name, business name, contact number, and service area</li>
  <li><strong>Subscription Records:</strong> Customer subscriptions, route data, and delivery schedules managed by the vendor</li>
  <li><strong>Payment Records:</strong> Daily, weekly, or monthly billing summaries</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. Location Data</h3>
<p>
  <strong>We collect your device location only to enable accurate milk delivery.</strong>
  Specifically, location is used to:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Save and confirm your delivery address</li>
  <li>Match you with nearby vendors offering home delivery</li>
  <li>Help vendors plan delivery routes for daily milk supply</li>
</ul>
<p>
  Location data is not used for advertising, third-party tracking, or any purpose
  unrelated to milk delivery operations. You can disable location access in your device
  settings at any time.
</p>

<h3>4. Device and Usage Information</h3>
<p>We automatically collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, app version</li>
  <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Features accessed, timestamps, and interaction patterns</li>
  <li><strong>Notification Preferences:</strong> Settings for delivery reminders and order alerts</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Provide Delivery Service:</strong> Manage your milk and dairy subscriptions, schedule deliveries, and ensure orders reach your address</li>
  <li><strong>Vendor Operations:</strong> Help local vendors manage their customers, routes, and daily delivery rounds</li>
  <li><strong>Send Notifications:</strong> Daily delivery reminders, payment dues, vendor updates, and subscription alerts</li>
  <li><strong>Improve the App:</strong> Analyze usage to enhance features and reliability</li>
  <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> Respond to queries, complaints, and refund requests</li>
  <li><strong>Security and Fraud Prevention:</strong> Detect and address unauthorized activity</li>
  <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Comply with applicable Indian laws including the IT Act, 2000</li>
</ol>

<hr />

<h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>

<h3>Storage</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Cloud Storage:</strong> Data is stored securely on Firebase / Google Cloud Platform</li>
  <li><strong>Local Cache:</strong> Some data is cached locally on your device for offline use</li>
  <li><strong>Sync:</strong> Information synchronizes between your device and our servers when online</li>
</ul>

<h3>Security Measures</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Secure authentication via Firebase Authentication</li>
  <li>Encrypted data transmission (HTTPS / TLS)</li>
  <li>Access controls limiting data to authorized personnel</li>
  <li>Regular security reviews and updates</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
<p>We do <strong>NOT</strong> sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>
<p>We share your information only in these circumstances:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Local Vendors:</strong> Your name, delivery address, and contact details are shared with the vendor fulfilling your milk subscription</li>
  <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Trusted third-party services (Firebase / Google) bound by confidentiality agreements</li>
  <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or government regulation</li>
  <li><strong>Protection of Rights:</strong> To protect the rights, property, or safety of XQ Tech Solutions, our users, or others</li>
  <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with merger, acquisition, or sale of assets (with prior notice)</li>
</ol>

<hr />

<h2>Your Rights and Choices</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Access:</strong> View your data stored in the App</li>
  <li><strong>Update:</strong> Modify your profile and address details at any time</li>
  <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Request deletion of your account and associated data (see <a href="/delete-request/field-fresh-milk">Delete Account</a>)</li>
  <li><strong>Location Control:</strong> Enable or disable location access via device settings</li>
  <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Control push notification preferences in app settings</li>
  <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> Stop using the App at any time</li>
</ol>
<p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@xqtechsolutions.com">admin@xqtechsolutions.com</a>.</p>

<hr />

<h2>Data Retention</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Account data is retained as long as your account is active</li>
  <li>Upon account deletion request, personal data is removed within 30 days</li>
  <li>Subscription and payment records may be retained per Indian tax and accounting laws</li>
  <li>Anonymized analytics data may be retained for service improvement</li>
  <li>Backup data may persist for up to 90 days before complete removal</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>
  Field Fresh Milk is not intended for use by children under 13. We do not knowingly
  collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have, please
  contact us immediately.
</p>

